                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A book about the REAL heroes/heroines of Civil Rights</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
